  "description": "The quiz assesses knowledge of HTML5 semantic elements, testing the ability to differentiate and correctly use tags beyond basic <div> and <span>. It is moderately challenging, presented in a playful, encouraging tone that nudges learners toward better markup practices. The style is informal and motivational, aiming to boost confidence while highlighting gaps.",
